  "description": "Rule 18 — produces sparse, isolated towers of activity. Seed 32768 (half-fill) creates balanced initial conditions. Square oscillator at warm mid-register. Slow step rate (2.5 Hz), medium scope (8) — the colony evolves at breathing pace, one visible step at a time. High sub level (0.6) grounds the texture. Low filter cutoff (2000 Hz) with moderate resonance makes each cellular event warm rather than bright. Simple and immediate — the organism as family instrument, accessible to any ear.",
